What is Video Profile? Simply talk about yourself, your family, preferences, passions, and everything that brings out the best in you through a self-shot video. How will it improve my profile? Video Profile adds credibility & authenticity to your profile. It increases your chances of getting more responses from other users, gives higher visibility and brings out the best in your profile. How do I shoot a great video? Make sure that the place you shoot your video in is well lit and audio is clear without any disturbances. Ask someone to hold the camera, ensure that the video is horizontal while shooting with a mobile phone. Do dress well, be comfortable, include family/ friends and feel free to speak in your mother tongue. But more than anything else, be yourself!
